        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer802018561" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12277463613758704467">Reminiscent of Perks Of Being A Wallflower, Love Letters To The Dead is too beautiful, too meaningful, and too heartbreaking to describe with words. An incredible, moving and very important story with a beating heart and bright soul. It&apos;s one of those books that everyone ought to read, own, and share with all their friends. <br/><br/>don&apos;t miss it</span>
  <span id="freeText12277463613758704467" style="display:none">Reminiscent of Perks Of Being A Wallflower, Love Letters To The Dead is too beautiful, too meaningful, and too heartbreaking to describe with words. An incredible, moving and very important story with a beating heart and bright soul. It's one of those books that everyone ought to read, own, and share with all their friends. <br /><br />don't miss it</span>
